ing: 1 cup fresh spinach, or to taste
1 cup frozen blueberries, or to taste
des: "I love this smoothie because it's so refreshing, easy to make, and extremely healthy!"
ins: Pour prune juice into a blender. Layer Greek yogurt, spinach, blueberries, strawberries, peach, and flax seeds in the blender, in this order. Start blender on low speed and gradually increase speed until smoothie is well blended.
